arguments.template:
<ng-template #elementTemplate>
        <ng-container *ngIf="data && visualData">
          <svg:g
          [attr.transform]="data.visualData > 0 ? 'rotate(' + data.visualData + ',' + getRotationCenterX() + ',' + getRotationCenterY() + ')' : ''"
          >
            <ng-container *ngFor="let s of data.objects; let i = index">
                <ng-container *ngIf="s.visible" dynamic-svg [componentData]="s" [overrideProperties]="overrideProperties" [elementId]="i + 1"
                  [hoverClass]="hoverClass"
                  (mouseDown)="onChildMouseDown($event)"
                  (mouseMove)="onChildMouseMove($event)"
                  (mouseUp)="onChildMouseUp($event)"
                  >
                </ng-container>
              </ng-container>
          </svg:g>
        </ng-container>
      </ng-template>
